content:
Activate Work Summaries for Voice Calls

To enable agents to generate and store voice call summaries, activate work summaries for voice calls.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
Edit (on Salesforce object) OR Modify All Data

From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Einstein Work Summaries, then select Einstein Work Summaries.
Click the Voice Calls tab.
To enable Work Summaries for voice calls, activate Voice Call Summaries.
title: Activating Work Summaries in Service Cloud
